{"data":[{"id":560718800,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"624836b266374237cebfe483aea4c170","url_token":"tulip2130","name":"WHite","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-08a0456a9305ce831879567686efe250_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-08a0456a9305ce831879567686efe250_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/624836b266374237cebfe483aea4c170","user_type":"people","headline":"为了未来，奋斗现在","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560718800","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545881716,"updated_time":1545881716,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e为什么很多人一定要这样去嘲讽，这只是一名高中生的热情，难道不应该指出他的错误，让他有更成熟明确的研究方向吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想那些冷言冷语的人一定是忘了自己高中时过着怎样的生活，至少在我的印象里，那是一段对什么事都充满好奇，渴望去发掘真相的岁月，不怕笑话，高中我一度沉迷量子理论，到处吹牛逼，但是到了大学，一方面是因为专业选了工科，另一方面是在大物中接触了实际的量子理论各种蛋疼公式后产生了退缩，于是老老实实继续做了个工科男，但是我心里对量子理论的热爱也从未熄灭，关注了科学院的一些公众号，有什么新发现都乐于去了解一下。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于题主我是有一些共鸣的，但我相信他的热情更甚于我，对此我的看法是，不要让你的梦因为知乎上的各路大佬泼冷水而熄灭，你能真正证明出哥猜甚至更多谜题的可能性一定是有的，现在只是个开始，不代表你是错的，只是你并没有真正的完成这份证明，还有许多细节需要进一步发掘，至于能否成功，就看你能否在短暂的人生中去捕捉到那微弱的希望。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e另外，上述所说的一切要建立在你读了一个还算过得去的大学，中国教育体制确实有其问题（否则法国学生也不至于集体游行反对建立全国统一招生录取平台），但是你现在需要做的是在这个体制下为自己争取到能更好实现你愿望的平台，暂时将这个哥德巴赫猜想证明的雏形放在一边，在这个人生最重要的考试中给出漂亮的结果是第一要事，否则真的进个二本三本，我想周围几乎没人愿意钻研的氛围里你也坚持不下去。嗯，能竞赛拿奖保送是最好的，这一点就算到了大学也不变，都在争着拿奖保研。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，如果你对于数学的热情和我一样，其实仅仅是浮于表面的简单了解，那这些终归会消退，想清楚后尽早站出来澄清，大家不会真的纠结于高中生尚且幼稚的梦，就像我，你其实仅仅是没有给这个梦的种子灌输足够的养分罢了，但你还有无数别的种子，人生会很精彩的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559412147,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8d58d1181437b55e07578490cd402381","url_token":"er-bao-zhu","name":"毛毛","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9cab26dec397eace096b5ad3bc1d8c31_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9cab26dec397eace096b5ad3bc1d8c31_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8d58d1181437b55e07578490cd402381","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559412147","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545724766,"updated_time":1545724766,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e可以看看华罗庚的经历：初中毕业以后，一边工作一边自学高中和大学低年级的全部数学课程。在杂志上发表了几篇数学论文，被清华大学数学系主任熊庆来看重，直接调到清华当图书管理员，第二年开始担任清华数学助理、然后是助教、讲师。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个初中文凭的天才，没有在清华读书，直接去清华当老师。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561984608,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9814fcef08486c982cd79d637936b825","url_token":"jing-chen-chen-29","name":"越努力越幸运","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-950e270b623c3d190562777ef156ee7f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-950e270b623c3d190562777ef156ee7f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/9814fcef08486c982cd79d637936b825","user_type":"people","headline":"命，是弱者的借口；运，是强者的谦词。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561984608","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546040743,"updated_time":1546040743,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主如果真的具有十几岁证明哥猜的能力，这样的数学天赋应该早就被发现了吧，少年天才嘛，也许几年前参加某某竞赛就可以一举成名，早就可以准备走竞赛保送的路子了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e个人认为，题主应该是数学知识体系以及对哥猜的认知尚浅，在自己的认知范围内认为证明没有问题，但是搞数学的应该一眼就能看出来问题所在。希望等公布证明以后，证明错了，你能虚心接受批评，放平心态，脚踏实地准备高考。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，如果，，如果被题主证明哥猜这种小概率事件发生了，那么也恭喜题主，希望保持初心，继续有所作为。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e等你公布结果，看看各位数学相关知乎er给的建议吧。还是奉劝一句，不要在不具有相匹配的实力的时候妄图走捷径，脚踏实地吧。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559800029,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"3ce3b6a6d09fa2cae7fbce5ed1bc59b9","url_token":"xiao-ze-ma-da-ha","name":"小泽马大哈","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/3cc371f8b_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/3cc371f8b_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/3ce3b6a6d09fa2cae7fbce5ed1bc59b9","user_type":"people","headline":"梦想是在北大办个设计学院，ENFP","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559800029","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545783125,"updated_time":1545783125,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e高中生真证出来的，那就是百年一遇不世出的天才，别说保送本科了，直接给教授职位估计都有可能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e假装证出来的，如果有一篇洋洋洒洒但是有漏洞的东西，包装包装还是可以用的，起码表明了对数学的兴趣和和一定基础，估计能够在自主招生过程中起到些作用，但直接保送可能比较难。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560638169,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"6f5c159eafe3defdb17b04b84c721cd1","url_token":"he-he-da-91-7","name":"Heisenberg","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f7a653ce57845993f9225143cb29b3dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/f7a653ce57845993f9225143cb29b3dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/6f5c159eafe3defdb17b04b84c721cd1","user_type":"people","headline":"Fiat Lux!","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560638169","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545875897,"updated_time":1545875897,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主你好，我从小学就开始研究这个问题了，我希望你能帮我改进一下这个结果：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=k%E6%98%AF%E6%97%A0%E5%B9%B3%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%A0%E5%AD%90%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%87%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8Cm%5Cne1%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%5C%5C+%5Cleft%7C+%5Csum_%7B%5Cchi_%7Bk%7D%7D%5E%7B%7D%7B%7D%5E%7B%2A%7D%7B%5Cchi_%7Bk%7D%28m%29%7D+%5Cright%7C%5Cleq%5Cleft%7C+%28m-1%2Ck%29+%5Cright%7C.\" alt=\"k是无平方因子的奇数，而m\\ne1时，有\\\\ \\left| \\sum_{\\chi_{k}}^{}{}^{*}{\\chi_{k}(m)} \\right|\\leq\\left| (m-1,k) \\right|.\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561690193,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fc8b0d2185e311c5c6aa76865c9a7168","url_token":"flute60564","name":"flute60564","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-63653259a0b4e91187d8014f36177851_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-63653259a0b4e91187d8014f36177851_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fc8b0d2185e311c5c6aa76865c9a7168","user_type":"people","headline":"延期狗/已毕业/非895毕业/年薪不到500k/房价不会崩/单反不会亡/求打脸","badge":[{"type":"identity","description":"教育学博士","topics":[]}],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561690193","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545989597,"updated_time":1545989597,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我真的是飘了，居然有人邀请我回答这种问题，我哪里回答过数学类的问题啊，关注问题好几天了，为什么要这时候邀请我啊~\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不是数学系的，只系统的学过微积分、线性代数和数理统计这些简单的课程，数学分析和数论都没有正式的学过，教材对我这种垃圾土博来说看起来也很难，学起来一点都不愉快。做个简单的，不太合适的类比，任何一个数学系的研究生来讲，如果能证明低二、三个档次的猜想，发篇AMC，嗯，一路畅通到二级教授，安家费年薪配偶工作加上任何需求，基本就是一生无忧了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是吧，我大概知道题主这句话什么意思，可以简单从这个角度讲一下。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这么说吧，这个问题火也不是没有道理的，知乎大部分用户都在15到35之间，大都受过，或者即将受高等教育。这也造成了知乎用户心气儿高、学历高、收入高、牛皮吹的响等一系列现象。但是哥猜的能力和保送的需求二者严重不对等，任何人如果有能力证明哥德巴赫猜想，那就是在世界顶峰，入选全世界教材，成为世界典范的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有这个能力的人，不会以“保送清北”为自己的奋斗目标。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主的需求翻译成大家的需求，大概是这么个意思：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大学版：如果我GPA 4.0，雅思10，托福120，能申请黑龙江东方学院的研究生么？\u003cbr\u003e研究生版：如果我一年能发一篇Nature和Science，够资格到海南软件职业技术学院工作么？\u003cbr\u003e普通人版：如果我年入上千万，能买得起我们县城的别墅么？\u003cbr\u003e疯子版：如果我找到了让人长生不老的药，卖50块钱一颗会不会太贵了？\u003cbr\u003e（如果有以上两所学校的师生看到了，我是随机百度的学校，无恶意，见谅）\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561060817,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"79084b0bbf92acd86e25ab7eabbb171d","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561060817","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545912425,"updated_time":1545912462,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果真的证明了，建议你忘记北大清华，了解一下菲尔茨奖\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e好好学习一下英语，法语中的一门\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e排名第二的巴黎大学被法国人教育改改搞来搞去的体系乱得很，不如考虑一下排名第四的巴黎高等师范学院，毕竟和别人说自己是傅里叶的校友不算很丢人的事情，对的，就是傅里叶变换的那个傅里叶\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cb\u003e世界各国菲尔兹奖人数[\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//zh.wikipedia.org/w/index.php%3Ftitle%3D%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%25B0%2594%25E5%2585%25B9%25E5%25A5%2596%26action%3Dedit%26section%3D4\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e编辑\u003c/a\u003e]\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e美国\u003c/a\u003e13\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259B%25BD\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e法国\u003c/a\u003e11\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e排名    大学                  菲尔兹奖总人数\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1    \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%25E5%2593%2588%25E4%25BD%259B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25A6\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e哈佛大学\u003c/a\u003e                   18\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2    \u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25BB%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25A6\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e巴黎大学\u003c/a\u003e                   16\